Dirty Reality Lab Publishing Rules

1. All research must start in:

/draft/reality/{id}/

2. Draft folders may contain:

summary.md
whitepaper_source.md
whitepaper.pdf
diagrams/*.svg

3. Public website content must live in:

/reality/{id}/

4. Public folders may only contain:

index.html
summary.html
whitepaper.pdf
diagrams/*.svg

5. Never publish markdown files to the public site.

6. Markdown must be converted to HTML before publishing.

7. The publishing process copies files from:

draft → reality

8. Homepage must only link to published realities.

9. Every published reality page (reality/{id}/index.html) must include Google Analytics tracking in <head>:

<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
<script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-SHC80VT5RE"></script>
<script>
  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
  gtag('js', new Date());
  gtag('config', 'G-SHC80VT5RE');
</script>

This is already included in reality_template.html — no manual action needed when using the publish script.

10. Every published reality page (reality/{id}/index.html) must include a subscribe form before the footer, using the template below. The form sends data to Google Sheets via Apps Script with source=lab.dirtyreality.net.

Subscribe form HTML (insert before <div class="footer">):

<hr>

<div class="subscribe-wrapper">
<div class="subscribe-label">Get new research delivered to your inbox.</div>
<form class="subscribe-form" onsubmit="handleSubscribe(event)">
    <input type="email" class="subscribe-input" placeholder="email@example.com" required>
    <button type="submit" class="subscribe-btn">Subscribe</button>
</form>
<div class="subscribe-msg"></div>
</div>

<hr>

Subscribe JS (insert before </body>):

<script>
function handleSubscribe(e) {
  e.preventDefault();
  var form = e.target;
  var email = form.querySelector('input').value;
  var msg = form.parentElement.querySelector('.subscribe-msg');
  var btn = form.querySelector('button');
  btn.disabled = true;
  btn.textContent = '...';
  var url = 'https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbxMbWXIe56bCpGt3oywPv_6NU8FH-UkMgkHbut3fxvneMF905yT4fKP9JLSlygbofNIhA/exec?email=' + encodeURIComponent(email) + '&source=lab.dirtyreality.net';
  fetch(url, { mode: 'no-cors' })
    .then(function() {
      form.style.display = 'none';
      msg.textContent = 'Subscribed! Thank you.';
    })
    .catch(function() {
      btn.disabled = false;
      btn.textContent = 'Subscribe';
      msg.textContent = 'Something went wrong. Please try again.';
    });
}
</script>